---
import WidgetWrapper from './WidgetWrapper.astro';
---

<WidgetWrapper>
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-8 text-center">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2">Volunteering Opportunities</h3>
    <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl">
      There are more ways to give in addition to financial support! While money helps, volunteers are the ultimate cause
      for the positive effects we make, and we always need more! If you would like to lend a hand, or both hands and
      join our team, please feel free to reach out at any time!
    </p>
  </div>
</WidgetWrapper>
